"31:23:14" : {s: 31, a: 23, w: 14, r: "", t: "بِذَاتِ", l: "ذُو", lc: 93, tl: "bithati", lb: "অধিকারী",e: "of what", b: "গুপ্ত বিষয়", f: 12, rm: ""},
"31:23:15" : {s: 31, a: 23, w: 15, r: "صدر", t: "ٱلصُّدُورِ", l: "صَدْر", lc: 44, tl: "l-ṣudūri", lb: "বক্ষ, সিনা, অন্তর",e: "(is in) the breasts", b: "অন্তরের", f: 15, rm: "To return from, come back, proceed, issue or emanate from, go forward, advance or promote, come to pass, happen, emanate from, strike on the chest/breast, commence. Anything that fronts, or faces one; hence breast, chest or bosom [often meaning his mind]. The fore part of anything. Going, or turning back and away."},
"31:24:1" : {s: 31, a: 24, w: 1, r: "متع", t: "نُمَتِّعُهُمْ", l: "مَّتَّعْ", lc: 18, tl: "numattiʿuhum", lb: "জীবিকা দেওয়া, উপভোগ করতে দেয়া, উপকৃত করা",e: "We grant them enjoyment", b: "তাদেরকে উপভোগ করতে দিবো", f: 1, rm: "to enjoy/benefit, gift, anything useful/advantageous, goods (e.g. utensils, furniture), a commodity."},
"31:24:2" : {s: 31, a: 24, w: 2, r: "قلل", t: "قَلِيلًۭا", l: "قَلِيل", lc: 70, tl: "qalīlan", lb: "ছোট, অল্প ",e: "(for) a little", b: "সামান্য", f: 55, rm: "to be few in number, small in quantity, rare. qalilun - few, little, small, rare, seldom. aqall - fewer, poorer. qallala - to appear as few."},
