"31:24:6" : {s: 31, a: 24, w: 6, r: "عذب", t: "عَذَابٍ", l: "عَذَاب", lc: 322, tl: "ʿadhābin", lb: "শাস্তি, আযাব, দুর্যোগ ",e: "a punishment", b: "শাস্তির দিকে", f: 13, rm: "chastisement, castigate, punishment, torture, torment, retribution, abstain/desist (e.g. from eating due to excessive thirst), relinquish, quit. To deny a thing, hinder anyone from, be inaccessible, prevent."},
